CHALLENGE BRIEF:

Build a Web Application called "Test Orchestrator" with following features:

✅ Core Features Required:

1️⃣ Jira Integration - Fetch User Stories directly from Jira

2️⃣ User Story Generator - Create enterprise level User Stories based on given template

3️⃣ Auto Test Plan Generation - Create comprehensive test plans based on fetched user stories and subtasks

4️⃣ Smart Test Case Creation - Automatically generate test cases from user story requirements

5️⃣ Output Dashboard- Display all generated deliverable(User Story / Test Plan / Test Case) in a clean, organized list

6️⃣ Code Generator - When user selects any test case, It Should Create Automation Code of selenium Or Playwright